# slacker

A slackbot that creates pivotal tracker stories when triggered

### Getting Started

* Get the code: `go get -u github.com/chendrix/slacker`
* Go to where the code was downloaded
* Copy the sample config: `cp ./config/fixtures/sampleConfig.yml config.yml`
* Edit `config.yml` and replace with your keys
* Run: `./bin/run`

### Running tests

* Bootstrap your development environment `./bin/bootstrap`
* Run tests `./bin/test`
